data.description: This adorable 3/2/1 home is perfect for the first time homebuyer, or downsizer! Inside this charmer, you will find a neutral, pleasing palette of color and a well-designed split plan layout which is cozy, yet functional. Additional features include CITY WATER, TILE FLOORING THROUGHOUT,  HUGE SCREENED-IN REAR LANAI, WRAP AROUND GUTTERS, VAULTED CEILINGS and a backyard with room for a pool.  This home is located just outside of North Port Estates, away from all the hustle and bustle of town, while still being less than a mile from the nearest fire station, and 3 miles from elementary, middle and high schools, churches, Morgan Activity Center and Aquatics Center, with pool, lazy river and water slides!  Access to I-75 is a breeze via Tropicaire Blvd to Sumter Blvd.
